This is a basic kit for creating a channel archive. This kit contains the menu page, as well as one video page. More video pages can be created to accomodate your channel's number of videos. The CSS is completely customizeable and the HTML tags are changeable using a text editor. Kit falls under the MIT License and is free to use. Providing the link to the original project is not compulsory but is greatly appreciated.

The owner(s) of this simple project are not responsible for stolen content or any misuse of this kit. This responsibility is on everyone who uses this kit.

Use cases:
-YouTube Channel Archive
-Video Project Archive
-Simple Video Gallery
